<% content_for :title do %>Home
<% end %>
<% content_for(:container_type) do %>skip
<% end %>
<div class="homepage">
  <div class="row first">
    <div class="over-text">
      <h2><br/>Endurance Event Data Lives Here</h2>
      <p>OpenSplitTime is a free resource built by endurance athletes for the ultra community. OpenSplitTime makes it
        easy to collect, store, and play with endurance event data.<br/>
        <% if current_user %>
          <br/>You are signed in. <strong>Scroll down to start exploring.</strong>
        <% else %>
          <strong>Join the community now.</strong>
        <% end %>
        <p/>

        <% if current_user %>
          <% if @presenter.recent_user_efforts.present? %>
            <h2>Your Recent Races</h2>
            <% @presenter.recent_user_efforts.first(2).each do |effort| %>
              <%= link_to effort.event_name, effort_path(effort), class: 'btn btn-info cta' %>
            <% end %>
            <br/>
          <% end %>

        <% else %>
          <form class="homepage-signup" name="homepage-signup" action="<%= new_user_registration_path %>">
            <div class="form-fields row clearfix">
              <div class="form-group col-xs-12 col-md-6">
                <input id="user_email" type="text" name="user[email]" placeholder="Email Address"/>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group col-xs-12 col-md-6">
                <input class="btn btn-info" type="submit" name="submit" value="Join the Community"/>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p>Already using
              OpenSplitTime? <%= link_to t('devise.sessions.new.sign_in'), '#', class: 'sign-in', data: {toggle: 'modal', target: '#log-in-modal'} %>
              <a href="<%= about_path %>" class="learn-more">Learn More</a></p>
          </form>
        <% end %>
        <br/>

        <h2>Recent Results</h2>
        <% @presenter.recent_event_groups(4).each do |event_group| %>
          <%= link_to event_group.name, event_group_path(event_group), class: 'btn btn-info cta' %>
        <% end %>
        </div>
    <div class="gradient"></div>
    <a data-controller="popover" data-theme="dark" data-placement="left" data-content="Traversing the west side of Isolation Peak, photo by Mark Oveson" class="photo-credit">Photo
      Credit</a>
  </div>
  <div class="row second">
    <div class="over-text">
      <%= image_tag("icons/icon-map.png", alt: 'Map Icon') %>
      <h2>Plan Your Efforts</h2>
      <p>Runners, pacers, families, and crews can use OpenSplitTime to plan for ultras. Just estimate your finish time
        and
        OpenSplitTime will suggest where you need to be and when.<br/>
        <strong>Hours of research converted to a few seconds? Yes please.</strong></p>
      <br/>
      <% @presenter.upcoming_courses(4).each do |course| %>
        <%= link_to course.name, plan_effort_course_path(course), class: 'btn btn-info cta' %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row third">
    <div class="over-text">
      <h2>Search the Archives</h2>
      <p>Browse and play with endurance event data like you've never done before. Analyze your efforts, discover
        your best segments, and find your peers. Much more is yet to come as the community gathers its data here.<br/>
        <strong>You can find every Hardrock effort ever run.</strong></p>
      <br/>
      <%= link_to 'Find Someone', people_path, class: 'btn btn-info cta' %>
      <%= link_to 'Search Hardrock Archives', organization_path('hardrock'), class: 'btn btn-info cta' %>
    </div>
    <div class="gradient"></div>
    <a data-controller="popover" data-theme="dark" data-placement="left" data-content="Descending from Grant-Swamp Pass, photo by Bill Wright" class="photo-credit">Photo
      Credit</a>
  </div>
  <div class="row fourth">
    <div class="over-text">
      <%= image_tag("icons/icon-timer.png", alt: 'Timer Icon') %>
      <h2>Open to Race Directors</h2>
      <p>We love to compete, but many of us don't love to organize. And the tools for tracking and organizing endurance
        events have been sorely lacking.<br/>
        <strong>All that has now changed.</strong></p>
      <br/>
      <%= link_to 'Import Event Data', getting_started_path, class: 'btn btn-info cta' %>
      <p><br/>(beta)</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row fifth">
    <div class="over-text">
      <h2>Unprecedented Live Tracking Tools</h2>
      <p>OST Live Entry is revolutionary. It learns from your time data. It gives you race progress for each aid
        station. It tells you instantly where your runners last reported, where they are due next, and who you ought to
        look for.<br/>
        <strong>Omniscience is pretty cool.</strong></p>
    </div>
    <div class="gradient"></div>
    <a data-controller="popover" data-theme="dark" data-placement="left" data-content="Running the North Inlet Trail in Rocky Mountain National Park, photo by Kari Fraser" class="photo-credit">Photo
      Credit</a>
  </div>
  <div class="row sixth">
    <div class="over-text">
      <h2>Endurance events change people.</h2>
      <p>They create hard challenges in a soft world. They bring us together when our natural inclination might be to
        wander alone. They help us feel the simple joys of food, warmth, and rest by exposing us to cold, hunger and
        discomfort. They help us realize how much more is buried within when we seem empty and dry.</p>
      <p><strong>Go git 'er done.</strong></p>
      <%= image_tag("icons/icon-s.png", alt: 'S Icon') %>
      <h1>OpenSplitTime.org</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>